Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是奇洛如給的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.22,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說可以拿去買\Nちぃ喜歡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.62,0:01:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ還是想送點東西給秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是書店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#09         ちぃ，購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.55,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多參考書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好多好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹有這本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.62,0:02:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹沒有這本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送這本給秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（只屬於我的人）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她堅持要一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不得已才讓她去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.28,0:02:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次才 發生過偷窺小屋事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也學會了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會不會迷路了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.36,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是不應該\N讓她自己一個人出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.27,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.77,0:03:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟明天都休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來邀你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就去啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.42,0:03:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我昨天才剛洗過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天有洗過\N難道今天就不用洗了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.63,0:03:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之來就是了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（健康中心          湯湯園）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間誰都不會來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是等於被我們包下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺很讚的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啦，還在擔心 嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.66,0:04:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是你讓她單獨出門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她也會講很多話了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，總之先進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.37,0:04:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有幫電腦洗澡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫…幫電腦洗澡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，原來你不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200元？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.61,0:04:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來電腦也要洗澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是常識，常識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常識？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.05,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好，所謂的幫電腦洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是指清潔的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清潔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.56,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是保養的一環\N是絕對不能偷懶的程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.06,0:04:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你也有幫電腦洗澡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.04,0:04:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為攜帶型的很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在家把她泡在清潔液中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她自己擦拭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為普通的電腦很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要到澡堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗完後就跟新的一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼帶ちぃ來就行了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你家的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不知道怎麼洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.06,0:05:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般是購買清潔軟體來安裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣電腦就能學會洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就能自己洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒錢買軟體啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.44,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪招？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己在這澡堂裡幫她洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我直接在這澡堂裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在這裡幫ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡意思就是說兩人都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.82,0:05:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在別人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脫…脫光光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.82,0:05:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是說真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你教她就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教什麼？當然是教她洗澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她有安裝學習軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教她之後她就會自己洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己就能到女浴池洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就只需要付澡堂費而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果變乾淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ一定也會很高興的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳平安回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，ちぃ買了東西…\N聽我說，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ買給秀樹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說妳是為了我去買東西的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹高興的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也會有開心 的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這種表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那叫笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑容？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是好事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這是幸福的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有禮物…雖然沒有那麼棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我要教妳做一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，教妳如何在澡堂洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.99,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是能讓身體乾淨的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到澡堂之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會先看到更衣室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的儲物櫃前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣脫下自己的衣服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.80,0:07:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先拆開禮物才對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹說過想要新的好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的澡堂就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，所謂的澡堂就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從獅子的開巴裡\N熱水嘩啦地流出…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，有好料的不高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我很高興啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，所謂的澡堂就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的澡堂就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我看到了那個以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的無法直接教ちぃ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想像力太豐富了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連線中，連線中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從那個站下載\N洗澡方法的檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之就交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用現在下載的檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓絲茉茉來示範
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的電腦來模仿就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在就跟著絲茉茉做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下載完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，執行剛才下載的檔案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.67,0:09:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.64,0:09:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.65,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是滾燙熱水澡堂的站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新…新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，不是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找教人洗澡的軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.46,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我可買不起軟體喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免費軟體就行了吧，不用錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下載完畢，執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,程式名稱“正確的洗澡禮節”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一，喝咖啡牛奶時手要叉著腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，再搜尋一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下載完畢，執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，重來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下載完畢，執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.64,0:10:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚到最後還是沒學會洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ要去打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.29,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我送妳到奇洛如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去昨天說的澡堂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等ちぃ打工回來就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我是本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，我是國分寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔，好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你今天下午有空嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天補習班沒課，所以沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想跟你談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.62,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.39,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有事想請教你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，在哪裡見面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.43,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就四點在車站前的多卡利昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地方嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣幫電腦洗澡才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.55,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.02,0:11:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天本來想請新保的電腦示範
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就是不順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有沒有什麼好辦法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和對ちぃ\N一個步驟一個步驟的教她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教她“洗澡的方法”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這招我試過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.88,0:12:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一直都不順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想買軟體的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想就只有這個方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是只有這個方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.06,0:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去澡堂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.29,0:12:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的表情好像很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，再努力教她一次看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.73,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不想歪，一定可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想歪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒事，沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我談什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，關於ちぃ的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前有說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.02,0:13:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會到自製機的BBS上留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人回應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓你知道一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BBS是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.80,0:13:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它類似網路上的告示版
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都可以在上面留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這麼方便的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，在那裡問洗澡的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定就可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.48,0:13:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？有人知道ちぃ的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人回覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.53,0:13:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回覆就是指 發表回覆文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些回覆內容都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我也想撿到這樣的電腦”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.97,0:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我想幫忙測試效能”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多是這類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也收到了一封郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附加了圖片檔案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附加檔案？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.21,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太清楚\N這跟ちぃ有沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.32,0:14:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片怎麼看都像是ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.13,0:14:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來很像ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.36,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這堆亂七八糟的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.57,0:14:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒看過這種接頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是惡作劇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某處看過ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拍下她的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後合成出這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.35,0:14:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過總覺得其中並不單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道寄信人是誰嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.22,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得郵件應該有\N所謂的“郵件地址”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不論寄幾次都被退了回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是已經沒被使用的地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是利用假地址寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.97,0:14:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.51,0:15:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是不想暴露身份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被手檔住的這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是“C”的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.82,0:15:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C、H、O、B、         I、T…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前應該跟你說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以“Chobits”為代號的\N那台傳說中的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠自己思考行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有人的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻又不是人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片真的是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.96,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ真的是那台\N叫作Chobits的超級電腦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.27,0:15:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來您想看什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.84,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來有這麼多種電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一起去澡堂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我現在來教妳\N洗澡的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要像這樣進去更衣室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂更衣室就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進澡堂後的第一間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那房間裡\N像這樣把衣服脫掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不必脫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著我來說明浴池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴池？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂浴池就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼大的東西裡\N裝著很多熱水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡進去會很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ知道這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這上面有浴池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ以前看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎麼洗澡了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在進浴池之前\N要先用肥皂洗身體喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就仔細看周圍然後跟著模仿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.48,0:17:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就待會見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也沒辦法再教她更多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.43,0:18:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當真的去做時\N常常會出乎意料的順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.46,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題，沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.17,0:18:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.33,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.34,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.68,0:18:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…你怎麼跑到男澡堂去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ模仿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看了周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了周圍，然後模仿了秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模仿秀樹，跟在後面進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是模仿我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去女澡堂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ要去這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ要跟秀樹一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，這次換洗這邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好有管理員小姐在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然還真不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐的這裡比ちぃ大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.28,0:19:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是秀樹的好料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還麻煩妳照顧ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要帶ちぃ去洗澡\N請隨時跟我說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，穿好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她穿起來真好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡還是最適合穿浴衣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡的事總算順利解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.77,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是稔給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.21,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.31,0:21:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.05,0:21:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒必要操這個心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次買的那本書的續集啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.85,0:21:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像又是一本很不可思議…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本書是ちぃ買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和秀樹的書一起買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.59,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ想要這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.02,0:21:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是ちぃ的薪水嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後妳想要什麼\N都可以去買喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.79,0:22:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的走在熟悉的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.80,0:22:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確會照映在眼簾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.71,0:22:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在成群結隊前進的人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.98,0:22:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那顆遭到淹沒         感到膽怯的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.69,0:22:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         像那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raison         d'etre         如同那般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.73,0:23:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑、沉沒、漂流\N究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.67,0:23:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著那把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.41,0:23:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的在尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.58,0:23:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.88,0:23:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那扇門的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ如果約會想去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.24,0:23:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.34,0:23:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能去剛到就要分開的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會地點要盡量挑選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.44,0:23:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓兩人長時間在一起的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.71,0:23:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書店？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.45,0:23:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.51,0:23:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人會變得很沉默的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.15,0:23:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會的訣竅在於與女伴的交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.35,0:23:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交談熱絡，氣氛也會跟著變好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.55,0:24:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.02,0:24:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泡妞手冊上是這麼寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.66,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，相遇」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.69,0:24:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管約會還是讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.93,0:24:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預習都很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.63,0:24:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
